          "settings": {
            "question": "What's your return/exchange policy?",
            "answer": "<p>We’re all about obsession. We pour our heart into every design. And all we want is for it to capture yours. We're sorry if your merch arrived damaged or if you got the wrong one. Just email us at honeyandblush.shop@gmail.com within 3 days with your order number and a photo. We’ll arrange a replacement or refund for you ASAP. Need more info? Read the whole policy <a href=\"/pages/refund-policy\" title=\"Refund Policy\">here</a>.<br/><br/></p>"
          }
