        "faq_item_C4AQD7": {
          "type": "faq_item",
          "settings": {
            "question": "Do you offer international shipping?",
            "answer": "<p>Yes, we do! Just an FYI: since our merch is made to order, the delivery may take a <em>little</em> longer than other brands.</p><p>Our merch is manufactured in the EU, but we also deliver to the UK, North America, and Oceania*. The delivery time depends on where you're located:</p><ul><li>EU & UK: 5–10 business days</li><li>Rest of the World: up to 15 business days</li></ul><p>Once your package has shipped, you will receive an email with the tracking information. And you'll stay updated on it's journey via email.</p><p>For fans ordering packages exceeding 150 euros to the rest of the world, watch out: customs fees will be applied to your order. In that case, you will be contacted either by the delivery company or the local customs office.</p><p>*We are not yet able to deliver everywhere in the world, but we promise, we're working on it.</p>"
          }
        },
